  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>BUBBLE BURSTING</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bubble Battle is designed for those craving an online/local party game experience reminiscent of the 80's and 90's. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players fly around with one simple objective: burst opponents’ bubbles before they burst yours. Collect powerups and out-maneuver opponents for fast-paced, addictive fun!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>BATTLE YOUR FRIENDS ONLINE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180520/extras/fc86186f77d8ec354327df208e982be1.poster.avif?t=1752196329\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180520/extras/fc86186f77d8ec354327df208e982be1.webm?t=1752196329\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180520/extras/fc86186f77d8ec354327df208e982be1.mp4?t=1752196329\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle it out with up to 4 players  online or locally.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>TEAM UP WITH FRIENDS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180520/extras/e2092491bd29c861ca3defe2e554b33e.poster.avif?t=1752196329\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180520/extras/e2092491bd29c861ca3defe2e554b33e.webm?t=1752196329\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180520/extras/e2092491bd29c861ca3defe2e554b33e.mp4?t=1752196329\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy 2 v 2 or a balanced 1 v 2 team mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >COLLECT POWERUPS AND WIN</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180520/extras/51bb65f8d96e2094ac1a8611267cfbaf.poster.avif?t=1752196329\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180520/extras/51bb65f8d96e2094ac1a8611267cfbaf.webm?t=1752196329\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180520/extras/51bb65f8d96e2094ac1a8611267cfbaf.mp4?t=1752196329\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use powerups to burst opponents' bubbles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Online lobby system - play friends or strangers in your region</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Easy to pick up and play  thanks to simple controls</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Quick gameplay - rounds are usually less than 2 minutes (the arena becomes smaller toward the end of a round)</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A selection of variants, powerups, and levels deliver many unique experiences</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
